headline: TikTok-fueled K-beauty boom triggers a retail race in the U.S.
summary: K-beauty has vaulted into the American mainstream, driven by TikTok and younger, more diverse shoppers. Retailers from Ulta to Walmart are racing to cash in.

headline: Talking Turkey: Lamb Is Expensive and It’s Not Just Tariffs.
summary: Domestic supplies of lamb have been shrinking for years. Imports, which have filled the gap for years, are declining.
